name: Custom Portrait
description:
Each portrait will be printed onto either A4 glossy or matte paper. It can be left black and white or coloured using watercolour or coloured digitally, according to what you request.

I can make portraits based off of someone you know, yourself, or even your favourite characters. After you've purchased a print, please send an email to kimberley_brooks@hotmail.com and we can discuss your order

name: Custom Paper Doll
description:
Each doll is hand made using 150gsm sketch book paper, brass paper fasteners and painted using water colour.

I can make a doll based off of someone you know, yourself, or even your favourite character. Send an email to kimberley_brooks@hotmail.com and we can discuss your order :)
